description: Freja eID Group AB is a SE-based company operating in Software industry. The company is headquartered in Upplands Vaesby, Stockholm and currently employs 47 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2014-12-18. Freja eID Group AB, formerly known as Verisec AB, is a Sweden-based information and technology company. The company operates the Freja eID e-identification and offers secure fulfillment services. This mobile application represents personal identity in digital form as an electronic identity (eID). Freja eID is the only e-ID in Sweden with the 'Svensk e-legitimation' quality mark - issued by the Swedish government's Agency for Digital Government DIGG.
